5
00:01:55,280 --> 00:02:01,100
♫ Looking at you, I forget to breathe ♫

6
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:08,010
♫This intimacy, even if we bicker,
it's with a mutual understanding♫

7
00:02:08,010 --> 00:02:12,360
♫ I want you to be my one and only ♫

8
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:18,350
♫ You are my one and only ♫

9
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:40,180
Well, I'll go retrieve the qin I repaired today.

10
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:44,730
Can... you play for me tonight?

11
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:48,180
- I can.
- Great.

12
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:54,720
By the way, this is for you.

13
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:15,530
♫ Light is casted in my eye by chance ♫

14
00:03:15,530 --> 00:03:23,130
♫ Just like how I came into your world by chance ♫

15
00:03:23,130 --> 00:03:30,410
♫ If the painting is beautiful, it's because of you ♫

16
00:03:30,410 --> 00:03:37,140
♫ If time turned back, would we meet again? ♫

17
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:41,060
♫ The most beautiful scenery of this life ♫

18
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:45,120
♫ is the clouds passing through the moonlight ♫

19
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:52,190
♫ Twisting and turning, I've fallen into your palm ♫

20
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:55,860
♫ The moon is covered; the moon is spotted ♫

21
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:59,600
♫ My treasured memories ♫

22
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:06,790
♫ and my simple feelings are difficult to write down ♫

23
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:10,340
♫ The moon rises as a lonely body; the moon sets as tears fall ♫

24
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:14,250
♫ It's me missing you ♫

25
00:04:14,250 --> 00:04:20,670
♫ Facing the moonlight, I say, "I'll wait for you" ♫

26
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,720
Then I'll... go back now.

27
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:41,250
Xiao Bao.

